How do we grow the game? Together. 

Watch our welcome video at the 2022 NFL FLAG Summit Presented by @sportsconnect.stack 🎥
Our man @dangerusswilson inspiring future ballers at the @NFLUK Flag Championships 🙌

@dangerusswilson growing the game 🇬🇧🙌 

#rg Our YOUTH is the greatest gift in the world! LONDON has been amazing watching the kids rock it for our @NFLFlag National Championship today in the UK & also working with the star studded kids @NFLAcademy Training Center! The Growth of the game is growing Exponentially & I’m glad to Partner with the @NFL to help make these kids Dreams come true Globally! To ALL the boys & girls in the world… ITS POSSIBLE! #WhyNotYou
Thanks @izellreese with our shared vision for flag & thanks Henry, Ben & everyone else to make this come to life! 
Thanks @jtheaps9 for helping coach the kids up with me today too!
